&lt;li&gt;Join the Rust community&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practice with small projects&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to open source&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;common-pitfalls-to-avoid&quot;&gt;Common Pitfalls to Avoid&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forgetting to make variables mutable&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fighting with the borrow checker&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
